From e5d944b4af63285cc5133d9619cc2a4722cb588d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Lorenzo Bianconi <lorenzo@kernel.org>
Date: Tue, 11 Mar 2025 18:45:05 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] wifi: mt76: mt7996: Add mt7996_sta_state routine
Git-commit: e5d944b4af63285cc5133d9619cc2a4722cb588d
Patch-mainline: v6.15-rc1
References: jsc#PED-14425

Introduce mt7996_sta_state routine in order to initialize wcid structure
in mt7996 codebase. This is a preliminary patch to enable MLO support in
MT7996 driver.

Signed-off-by: Lorenzo Bianconi <lorenzo@kernel.org>
Link: https://patch.msgid.link/20250311-mt7996-mlo-v2-6-31df6972519b@kernel.org
Signed-off-by: Felix Fietkau <nbd@nbd.name>
Acked-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

---
 drivers/net/wireless/mediatek/mt76/mac80211.c |   5 +-
 drivers/net/wireless/mediatek/mt76/mt76.h     |   2 +
 .../net/wireless/mediatek/mt76/mt7996/main.c  | 100 +++++++++++++++---
 .../net/wireless/mediatek/mt76/mt7996/mmio.c  |   3 -
 .../wireless/mediatek/mt76/mt7996/mt7996.h    |   6 --
 5 files changed, 91 insertions(+), 25 deletions(-)

